m/clip/16389596/harvard_wins_at_football_her_team_has/|via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}</ref>\n\n|November 17|at|[[1883 Princeton Tigers football team|Princeton]] ([[Harvard\u2013Princeton football rivalry|rivalry]])|[[University Field (Princeton)|University Field]]|[[Princeton, NJ]]|L 7\u201326| |<ref>{{cite news|title=Two Games of Football: Princeton Defeats Harvard and Yale Overwhelms Columbia|newspaper=The Sun (New York)|date=November 18, 1883|page=10|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/15270808/two_games_of_football_princeton_beats/|via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}</ref>\n\n|November 22| |[[1883 Michigan Wolverines football team|Michigan]]|Jarvis Field|Cambridge, Massachusetts|W 3\u20130|500|<ref>{{cite web|title=1883 Football Team|publisher=University of Michigan, Bentley Historical Library|accessdate=January 9, 2018|url=http://bentley.umich.edu/athdept/football/fbteam/1883fbt.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=College Foot-Ball: An Unfinished Game Between Harvard and Michigan Elevens|newspaper=The New York Times|date=November 23, 1883|page=5|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/20553620/?terms=harvard%2Bmichigan|via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}</ref>\n\n|November 29|vs|[[1883 Yale Bulldogs football team|Yale]] ([[Harvard\u2013Yale football rivalry|rivalry]])|[[Polo Grounds]]|[[New York, NY]]|L 2\u201323|nearly 10,000|<ref>{{cite news|title=Yale Again Victorious|newspaper=New York Tribune|date=November 30, 1883|page=8|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/16316816/yale_again_victorious/|via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Harvard Crimson football navbox}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1883 Harvard Crimson Football Team}}\n[[Category:1883 college football season|Harvard]]\n[[Category:Harvard Crimson football seasons]]\n[[Category:1883 in sports in Massachusetts|Havard]]\n\n\n{{collegefootball-1880s-season-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Jweiss11", "label": "safe", "comment": "cleanup infobox, cat sort key", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1883_Harvard_Crimson_football